This paper is about reinforcement learning, which is a subfield of machine learning. The paper discusses the challenges of implementing, executing, and testing reinforcement learning tasks, which are common issues in the field of deep learning. Therefore, the most likely sub-category is cs.LG (Machine Learning), followed by cs.AI (Artificial Intelligence) and cs.DC (Distributed, Parallel, and Cluster Computing). The paper also discusses the issue of distributed communication patterns, which suggests that it may be relevant to the sub-categories cs.SY (Systems and Control) and cs.NE (Neural and Evolutionary Computing).
